**Poll Manipulation** | Ability Type
__Basics__
This is the ability to modify polls themself in some way. This comes in several forms.
__Details__
This ability can affect one of five things related to polls:
• Addition: add a new poll to an already existing one
• Creation: The role itself is what causes the poll to exist
• Cancellation: After the poll has been closed, the resulting effect is cancelled
• Deletion: Remove a poll that was supposed to otherwise exist
• Candidate Manipulation: Modify the results of the poll
